>\n<br />\n所以奇怪<br />\n<br />\n陰謀論咁諗可能有後著</blockquote><br />\n因為唔<span style=\"color: red;\">少</span>雙非家長只係貪個港藉<br />\n而且近年佢地得到既學校資訊多左，有d寧願係深圳讀都唔想讀香港差既學校<br />\n<br />\n最重要身份證已經拎左<br />\n隨時可以再去香港讀書做野<br />\n呢個政策係方便佢地兩邊走</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cc83703f28324b698533b59bfcebf2d86eb93003","tid":387844,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所謂嘅港籍，好可能係有香港身份證但喺大陸住嘅新殖民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼雙非唔使爭學位<br />\n<br />\n但講真黎得香港又點會想番大陸讀<br />\n咁落黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以奇怪<br />\n<br />\n陰謀論咁諗可能有後著</blockquote><br />\n因為唔<span style=\"color: red;\">少</span>雙非家長只係貪個港藉<br />\n而且近年佢地得到既學校資訊多左，有d寧願係深圳讀都唔想讀香港差既學校<br />\n<br />\n最重要身份證已經拎左<br />\n隨時可以再去香港讀書做野<br />\n呢個政策係方便佢地兩邊走</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b7a8b9c069daba03bfe3992ee02362db4b7fc5","tid":387844,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本地學校都收唔夠人<br />\n仲有學生去大陸讀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時統一派位會派你過去入讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔會<br />\n想家長暴動咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今時今日政府會驚暴動咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c9539881d0f63f4aa4dacc50340313eea05954","tid":387844,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05